<p>Late Saturday, the president used the tragedy in Parkland to <a href="http://www.thenewcivilrightsmovement.com/ryanjent/trump_uses_parkland_mass_shooting_to_attack_fbi_forrussia_investigation">attack the FBI</a> for the Russia investigation. It was just one of the many, many tweets in the president‚Äôs most recent <a href="http://www.thenewcivilrightsmovement.com/ryanjent/trump_ends_saturday_begins_sunday_with_public_meltdown_over_russia">public meltdown</a>.</p>
